00:44:16.910 --> 00:44:20.910
your read proc for that input port,
no matter how many

00:44:20.910 --> 00:44:24.650
input ports you create,
all of those read procs get serviced

00:44:24.660 --> 00:44:27.110
by a single high-priority thread.

